{
  "stem": "21437.9",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So he said, look, this is all pregnancy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You know, he sort of made a few this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he sent me home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then that was on-- like, I was going every Friday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then that was about Wednesday, or Tuesday-- I suddenly-- I got up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I didn't feel anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And that was-- but it was still like the same, like before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But on Friday, by the time I went on Friday, it was apparently-- it was already obvious to-- to even-- with a-- you could see it with a naked eye, that everything dropped.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So you know, the baby must have been already, you know, for quite a few days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But it was not detected.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And my husband nearly killed him, the doctor, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He got-- he came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he was outraged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I think that this-- having a sister here, and being disappointed, and I was very ill for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was, again, a doctor, who took care of me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if it wouldn't be for this doctor, I wouldn't be allowed to come to Australia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is how we-- you know, it evolved.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For me, I sort of-- as hurt as I was, as disappointed as I was, I think I could separate those two feelings, you know, that Israel was Israel, and people was people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But for-- for a lot of people, the people from this country, this is what they represent, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- So how did you get to Australia?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came by boat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Would you believe that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just know we went by boat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think that this was something like we arrived in Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
